"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"US President Donald Trump gave a speech where he talked about his political plans and also honored war veterans and American history.\",            \"english_title\": \"Trump's Speech\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de Estados Unidos, Donald Trump, dio un discurso donde habl\u00f3 sobre sus planes pol\u00edticos y tambi\u00e9n honr\u00f3 a los veteranos de guerra y la historia de Am\u00e9rica.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Discurso de Trump\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelensky says the goal is to target important infrastructure that makes money for Russia's war.\",            \"english_title\": \"Zelensky's Goal\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de Ucrania, Volodymyr Zelensky, dice que el objetivo es atacar infraestructura importante que hace dinero para la guerra de Rusia.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Objetivo de Zelensky\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Marine Le Pen, a far-right leader, is trying to overturn a decision that found her guilty of using EU funds wrongly.\",            \"english_title\": \"Le Pen's Legal Battle\",            \"translated_version\": \"Marine Le Pen, una l\u00edder de extrema derecha, est\u00e1 tratando de cambiar una decisi\u00f3n que la encontr\u00f3 culpable de usar mal fondos de la UE.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Batalla Legal de Le Pen\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The Pope honored migrants who died at sea at a cemetery on the Italian island of Lampedusa.\",            \"english_title\": \"Pope Honors Migrants\",            \"translated_version\": \"El Papa honr\u00f3 a los migrantes que murieron en el mar en un cementerio en la isla italiana de Lampedusa.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Papa Honra a Migrantes\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A storm is expected to bring very strong winds and high waves when it hits land on Monday.\",            \"english_title\": \"Storm Warning\",            \"translated_version\": \"Se espera que una tormenta traiga vientos muy fuertes y olas altas cuando llegue a tierra el lunes.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Advertencia de Tormenta\"        }    ]}"